    "description": {
      "paragraphs": [
        "BunnyEra was forged in the belief that creation should feel like commanding a terminal—precise, powerful, and infinitely modular. We rejected the cluttered, bloated builders of the past. In their place, we built an OS-shell aesthetic that respects your craft.",
        "Every section is a module. Every module is sovereign. Drag, drop, and deploy with the confidence of a developer and the vision of a designer. No code required. No limits imposed.",
        "From the neon-accented dark console to the soft glow of our UI components, every pixel serves a purpose. This is digital sovereignty—your ideas, your rules, your domain."
